{"tid":2188665,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國波特蘭上周末槍擊案疑犯被警擊斃　曾辯稱當日開槍自衛","createTime":"2020-09-04T11:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T11:57:56.000Z","uid":198278,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27b5bad1c39c40c9e3efff36877471086066d2ff","tid":2188665,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"2020-09-04 HKT 17:38<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547882-20200904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547882-20200904.htm&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cWE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=18bbbafc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547882-20200904.htm&h=5de302e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547882-20200904.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國俄勒岡州波特蘭市的反種族歧視及反警暴示威持續。涉嫌在上周末的示威中，槍殺一名右翼份子的疑犯，被聯邦執法人員開槍擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯是48歲男子雷諾爾，警方交代案情時指出，監視雷諾爾期間發現他離開一間屋，登上汽車，警員上前截查。疑犯落車逃走，手上有武器，4名在場警員都有開槍。<br />\n<br />\n波特蘭市上周末有示威者，與總統特朗普的支持者衝突，期間一名右翼組織成員胸部中槍死亡。雷諾爾是當地抗警暴示威常客，槍擊案後他曾經在社交網頁及向傳媒表示，開槍是為了自衛，別無選擇。"},{"pid":"904361f110dd05418f7bc95b2f974a2bd3054f42","tid":2188665,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5407d69e3aba7e24dce19aaf81781bc2e9c9d86","tid":2188665,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb2622ea92755d5696a9119492a44b7dfadf38d","tid":2188665,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\